  "faq": {
    "id": "faq",
    "eyebrow": "FAQ",
    "headline": "Questions, answered.",
    "items": [
      {
        "q": "Is Chika Chika Cool safe to swallow?",
        "a": "Yes. The formula is 100% natural, contains no chemical preservatives, and is intentionally designed to be added to drinking water. There is no rinsing required after direct application."
      },
      {
        "q": "How long until I see results?",
        "a": "Most pet owners report visibly fresher breath within 3-7 days of daily use. Reduction in plaque and gum inflammation typically becomes visible within 2-3 weeks. For performance animals, the analgesic effect on bit-related discomfort is often immediate."
      },
      {
        "q": "Will this affect a racing animal's pre-race screening?",
        "a": "No. Chika Chika Cool contains no banned substances. All seven herbal ingredients and the grapefruit seed extract preservative are confirmed as zero-doping. The product is safe for daily use through training and competition."
      },
      {
        "q": "What's the difference between the 100ml and 1L bottles?",
        "a": "Same formula, different sizes. The 100ml is sized for one or two companion pets and lasts approximately 2-3 months of daily use. The 1L is sized for stable and racing operations and is designed to be added to large drinking troughs across multiple animals."
      },
      {
        "q": "How do I get my dog or cat to accept the spray?",
        "a": "Start by mixing 5-10 sprays into 100ml of drinking water for the first 1-2 weeks. Once they're used to the herbal taste, transition gradually to direct application. Some pets never fully accept direct spraying — and that's fine. Continued use through drinking water delivers the same benefits."
      },
      {
        "q": "Can puppies, kittens, or pregnant animals use it?",
        "a": "Yes, the formula is gentle enough for animals of all life stages. As with any new product, we recommend introducing it gradually and consulting your veterinarian if your animal has specific health conditions."
      },
      {
        "q": "Is it safe for cats specifically?",
        "a": "Yes. Many natural pet products contain ingredients (like xylitol, certain essential oils, or alcohol) that are toxic to cats. Chika Chika Cool contains none of these. The herbal formula is safe for feline use."
      },
      {
        "q": "How is the product shipped internationally?",
        "a": "We ship globally for both retail and bulk B2B orders. International orders are typically processed within 3-5 business days from our Seoul facility. Contact us for shipping costs to your region and for distributor pricing."
      },
      {
        "q": "Can I become a distributor in my country?",
        "a": "Yes. We're actively expanding our global distribution network, with a particular focus on the GCC, North America, and Southeast Asia. Bulk pricing and exclusive territory agreements are available. Use the contact form below to start the conversation."
      },
      {
        "q": "What's the shelf life?",
        "a": "Two years from manufacture date when stored at room temperature in the original sealed bottle. Once opened, use within 12 months for best efficacy. The grapefruit seed extract acts as a natural preservative throughout the shelf life."
      }
    ]
  },

